<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 09:16:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>亚洲黄金印度经销商提供折扣；中国需求季节性疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-indian-dealers-offer-discounts-china-sees-seasonally-soft-demand-2024-12-06/</link><description>印度的实物黄金六周来首次打折出售，因为卢比走软推高了价格，进而抑制了需求，而最大消费国中国的需求出现季节性放缓。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 08:13:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-indian-dealers-offer-discounts-china-sees-seasonally-soft-demand-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>NBA与澳门赌场金沙中国签署多年协议，在澳门赌博中心进行比赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/basketball/nba-inks-multi-year-deal-with-macau-casino-sands-china-play-gambling-hub-2024-12-06/</link><description>美国国家篮球协会（NBA）与澳门赌场运营商金沙中国签署了一项多年期协议，在澳门举行季前赛，此举是在当局敦促赌场业多元化、远离赌博之际采取的。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 06:52:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/basketball/nba-inks-multi-year-deal-with-macau-casino-sands-china-play-gambling-hub-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>越南对美国贸易顺差飙升引发对特朗普关税的新担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnams-soaring-us-trade-surplus-stokes-new-fears-trump-tariffs-2024-12-06/</link><description>行业高管和分析师表示，由于数据显示越南对美国的贸易顺差不断膨胀，越南很容易成为特朗普新政府的下一个关税目标。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 06:34:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnams-soaring-us-trade-surplus-stokes-new-fears-trump-tariffs-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：风险警惕的市场倒计时就业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-12-06/</link><description>Stella Qiu 展望欧洲和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 05:39:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>报道：中国将举办2019年以来首场NBA季前赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/reports-china-set-host-first-nba-preseason-games-since-2019-2024-12-06/</link><description>据周四的多份报道称，NBA 与中国的关系在 2019 年因总经理的一条推文而变得冷淡，但随着周五宣布将于 10 月在澳门举行两场季前赛，NBA 与中国的关系显然正在解冻。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 05:38:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/reports-china-set-host-first-nba-preseason-games-since-2019-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>在预期的战争游戏之前，台湾敦促中国“松开拳头”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/ahead-expected-war-games-taiwan-urges-china-unclench-its-fists-2024-12-06/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德周五敦促中国“松开拳头”，不要采取任何单方面行动，并在预计中国将在台湾举行军演之前表示，北京不会通过军事演习赢得任何尊重。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 03:56:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/ahead-expected-war-games-taiwan-urges-china-unclench-its-fists-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾在南海对峙后与盟友举行演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/united-states-japan-philippine-conduct-maritime-exercises-south-china-sea-2024-12-06/</link><description>菲律宾军方周五表示，菲律宾与美国和日本在南海专属经济区内举行海上演习，两天前，菲律宾与北京围绕争议浅滩发生海上对峙。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 02:25:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/united-states-japan-philippine-conduct-maritime-exercises-south-china-sea-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市对韩国风险持谨慎态度，美元在就业数据公布前保持警惕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-06/</link><description>由于韩国的政治骚乱打压市场情绪，周五大多数亚洲股市下跌，而美元多头焦急地等待美国就业数据是否会挑战或巩固本月降息的预期。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 02:18:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普任命前参议员戴维·珀杜为驻华大使</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-says-he-picks-former-senator-david-perdue-be-ambassador-china-2024-12-06/</link><description>珀杜是来自佐治亚州的共和党人，曾于 2015 年至 2021 年担任参议院议员，此前他在香港担任了 40 年的企业高管。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 02:14:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-says-he-picks-former-senator-david-perdue-be-ambassador-china-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>最新数据显示，印度从中国的钢铁进口量创历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-steel-imports-china-hit-record-high-latest-data-shows-2024-12-06/</link><description>路透社查阅的临时政府数据显示，从四月份开始的本财年前七个月，印度从中国的成品钢材进口量创下历史新高，令数百家印度小型钢铁生产商感到不安。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 00:21:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-steel-imports-china-hit-record-high-latest-data-shows-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：印度利率调整成为焦点，政治危机降温</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-12-05/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 21:48:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>通用汽车表示，洛登将领导凯迪拉克 F1 车队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/lowdon-lead-cadillac-f1-team-gm-says-2024-12-05/</link><description>通用汽车及其合作伙伴 TWG Global 周四表示，计划于 2026 年进入一级方程式赛车的新凯迪拉克车队已任命前玛鲁西亚首席执行官格雷姆·洛登 (Graeme Lowdon) 为负责人。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 21:10:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/lowdon-lead-cadillac-f1-team-gm-says-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>FCC主席提出网络安全规则以应对中国盐台风电信黑客攻击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/fcc-chair-proposes-cybersecurity-rules-response-chinas-salt-typhoon-telecom-hack-2024-12-05/</link><description>美国联邦通信委员会主席杰西卡·罗森沃塞尔 (Jessica Rosenworcel) 在周四的一份声明中表示，该机构提议要求通信服务提供商提交年度认证，证明他们已制定计划来防范网络攻击。该提案在一定程度上是为了回应据称由北京支持的黑客组织“Salt Typ”的努力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 20:17:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/fcc-chair-proposes-cybersecurity-rules-response-chinas-salt-typhoon-telecom-hack-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>巴拉圭因台湾“干涉”驱逐中国特使</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/paraguay-expels-chinese-envoy-over-interference-domestic-affairs-2024-12-05/</link><description>巴拉圭周四表示，已取消一名中国低级外交官的签证，并命令他离开，此前这位特使似乎鼓励立法者重新考虑巴拉圭与台湾的友好关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 19:53:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/paraguay-expels-chinese-envoy-over-interference-domestic-affairs-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>习近平强调要在军队中反腐败</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-xi-stresses-need-fight-graft-military-2024-12-05/</link><description>据中央电视台周四报道，中国国家主席习近平强调，要加强军队纪律建设、反腐败斗争，并提高信息战能力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 10:58:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-xi-stresses-need-fight-graft-military-2024-12-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>